{"tid":1744293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[集氣]天水圍中彈少年","createTime":"2019-11-21T15:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T06:36:00.000Z","uid":338636,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b828ed6647429cc6f4f261a4aeb20c60f20d5c","tid":1744293,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"//天水圍15歲姓傅嘅少年喺11月13號俾黑警開出嘅TG彈擊中頭部後重創，即晚入院進行開腦手術後，情況都未見有好轉。直到今日，傅同學情況仍然危殆，需要喺ICU留醫⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n黑警除咗用TG打中少年頭部之外 ，黑警仲有好多好多惡行，係香港人一世都唔可以忘記。同時，今日係元朗7.21鄉黑恐襲第四個月，警黑合作，令香港寫下最黑暗嘅歷史；呢一切一切，都唔可以原諒、唔可以忘記。面對黑警惡行，香港人唔可以善忘。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1548599625279052&amp;id=635086113297079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1548599625279052%26id%3D635086113297079&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt86nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a6e26f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1548599625279052&amp;id=635086113297079</a><br />\n<br />\n已經成個禮拜喇<br />\n聰仔嘅情況依舊係危殆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登好似冇咩人講<br />\n大家可唔可以一齊為佢打打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢渡過危險期"},{"pid":"a9c7ae75d210973cc842004a1a1a13d40fb188dd","tid":1744293,"uid":338636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7RtTBPOLLvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7RtTBPOLLvY&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt86nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a32a118f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7RtTBPOLLvY</a><br />\n<br />\n好想播俾聰仔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159dc11e05d8ff2f92bf05bca0810b2252714dc7","tid":1744293,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"手足不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji